{"tid":121719,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[急尋目擊者] 「暴動」案再要搵證人","createTime":"2017-02-15T12:42:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T14:49:16.000Z","uid":66607,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da47880b99fa29a4aa9f2e2c9613c9350db28f04","tid":121719,"uid":66607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:42:55.000Z","msg":"[[急尋目擊者]]<br />\n依家喺區域法院審理緊年初一既「暴動」案 <br />\n希望盡快搵到目擊者見到以下相關情節請聯絡事主<br />\n事主好急需要證人證明警察講大話同對事主作出暴力恐嚇 <br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n2016年2月9日凌晨4:50 至 5:15 在彌敦道北行線 近創興廣場(對面係信和)<br />\n當時警方在彌敦道近花槽拘捕左一名長髮藍衫人士 並帶到北行線行人路上店鋪鐵閘外 <br />\n有幾名警員圍住長髮藍衫人士(佢係蹲下) 有警員大力將藍衫人頭部撞向鐵閘數次 <br />\n藍衫人曾經大叫「警察打人」 。 <br />\n當時藍衫人見到對面南行線近花槽 (即信和外) 有不少人聚集 <br />\n希望有目擊者幫忙, 感激 ! ! !<br />\n<br />\n對本案十分關鍵 , 請幫忙share! 並希望如有目擊者請在明天(16/2) 9:00am 前聯絡事主<br />\nTelegram username: iambello15 <br />\nemail: iambello15@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n以下片段(26:09) 當時彌敦道情況, 可參考。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l45jpOytAUc&amp;index=7&amp;t=1764s&amp;list=PLjtJxhkxXGsRBUa00o_RsvaxjwGRmr0zB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dl45jpOytAUc%26index%3D7%26t%3D1764s%26list%3DPLjtJxhkxXGsRBUa00o_RsvaxjwGRmr0zB&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjVzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=4fe94f67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l45jpOytAUc&amp;index=7&amp;t=1764s&amp;list=PLjtJxhkxXGsRBUa00o_RsvaxjwGRmr0zB</a>"},{"pid":"19db26ce4831dcd19e4d604f57255027c053ca60","tid":121719,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:44:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06f39a882c37c6bf2c6231af646679a806543d05","tid":121719,"uid":38784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:44:27.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"0e0a38ccf558f32ce284888bb7a45fde2338488b","tid":121719,"uid":33644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:45:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cf900747ea6409191e6d